%description
FRR is free software which manages TCP/IP based routing protocols.
It supports BGP4, BGP4+, OSPFv2, OSPFv3, IS-IS, RIPv1, RIPv2, RIPng,
PIM and LDP as well as the IPv6 versions of these.

FRR is a fork of Quagga..

